    <briefdescription>
<para>Component that holds transformation data (position, rotation, scale). </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1modules_1_1spatial_1_1transform_1_1components_1_1TransformComponent" kindref="compound">TransformComponent</ref> manages the spatial state of a GameObject. It stores the local transform (relative to parent) and the computed world transform. Changes to local properties mark the component as dirty, signaling systems to recompute the world transform. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
